ironmental footprint, appealing to sustainability-conscious buyers.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-kMriOJ bmOeBq pf-79_ pf-text-1"><strong>Ethical: </strong>Guaranteed conflict-free.<br><span style="color: rgb(208, 2, 27);"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Learn More: <a href="https://www.igi.org/lab-grown-diamonds-vs-natural-diamonds/lab-grown-vs-natural-diamond/" target="_blank">Lab-Grown Diamonds vs. Natural Diamonds</a></span></span></li></ul><h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cmaqZA fXrIOS pf-81_ pf-heading-1-h2">Exploring Non-Diamond Engagement Rings</h2><p class="sc-kAkozD iOjmJ pf-83_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">If you’re open to alternatives, non-diamond engagement rings can be equally stunning and even more budget-friendly.</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cmaqZA fXrIOS pf-85_ pf-heading-1-h3">Popular Alternatives</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-fulBNO eRdNQN pf-87_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-kMriOJ bmOeBq pf-88_ pf-text-1"><strong>Moissanite: </strong>Known for its brilliance and durability, moissanite is a top diamond alternative.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-kMriOJ bmOeBq pf-90_ pf-text-1"><strong>Sapphires:</strong> Available in many colors, sapphires are timeless and durable.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-kMriOJ bmOeBq pf-92_ pf-text-1"><strong>Rubies &amp; Emeralds: </strong>Vibrant and luxurious options for those seeking colorful gemstones.<br></li></ul><img alt="1121-neoshine-blog配图_Affordable Diamond Engagement Rings- Quality and Style for Every Budget 副本 4.jpg__PID:5d53312f-c539-4605-9966-b3b1a61c85af" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0897/6921/4241/files/1121-neoshine-blog__Affordable_Diamond_Engagement_Rings-_Quality_and_Style_for_Every_Budget_4.j